node.text:
“THE CALM BEFORE THE STORM” 
-
The storm clouds are puff printed to give a 3D “cloud” effect and the flames on “NOTHING BUT RED” are also puff printed. All dyed pieces will be printed on our 11.5oz heavyweight blank.
-
This is PART 2 of the WESTERN PULP series. Each piece will come with its own “private” trading card that reveals the short backstory of the character or scene. I will not be post these cards online and I encourage purchasers not to post them either.

node.text:
“SOME DEMONS AREN’T WORTH FIGHTING”
-
This shirt blank is a god damn crowning achievement for us. It’s an 11.5 oz cotton jersey that feels like those heavy-weight Snoop Dogg Vetements t-shirts. I’m telling you right now, may I get struck by lightning if I’m exaggerating, this is one best quality shirts I’ve ever touched with my callused, stubby fingers. This is what we’ll be using for our dyed blanks from now on. Black shirts and hoodies will remain the same.
-
This will be a part of the WESTERN PULP series. Each piece will come with its own “private” trading card that reveals the short backstory of the character or scene. I will not be post these cards online and I encourage purchasers not to post them either.

“IF YOU WERE SEVERELY DEHYDRATED OUTSIDE OF LAS VEGAS, NEVADA”
-
7/18
5PM EST 2PM PST
-
This collection will consist only of tie dye, stone washed and garment dyed pieces. If you were on the brink of death in the Mojave desert after a family vacation in Vegas and you’d step over your own grandmother’s dead body for a single droplet of water, these pieces are what you’d see
